'''麥爾斯·亞歷山大·泰勒'''（{{lang-en|Miles Alexander Teller}}，{{bd|1987年|2月20日}}）<ref>https://twitter.com/Miles_Teller/status/436587509401661440</ref><ref>http://variety.com/2014/film/news/miles-teller-feels-a-new-beat-at-this-years-sundance-1201066289/</ref>是一位[[美國|美國]]男演員和音樂家。他主演的电影包括《{{le|戀夏進行式|The Spectacular Now}}》、《[[爆裂鼓手|爆裂鼓手]]》、《[[分歧者系列電影|分歧者系列電影]]》、《[[火線掏寶|火線掏寶]]》、 《{{le|熱血狂拳|Bleed for This}}》、《[[感謝您為國效力_(電影)|感謝您為國效力]]》<ref>{{cite web| url= https://variety.com/2014/film/news/miles-teller-feels-a-new-beat-at-this-years-sundance-1201066289/|title=Miles Teller on his Breakout 'Whiplash' Role and Blushing for Nicole Kidman|work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]| first=Ramin |last= Setoodeh|date=2014-01-23 | access-date= 2017-06-19|quote=Teller, 26...}}</ref>和《[[捍衛戰士：獨行俠|捍衛戰士：獨行俠]]》<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Top Gun: Maverick’s Miles Teller On Inheriting Goose’s Iconic Moustache – Exclusive Image|url=https://www.empireonline.com/movies/news/top-gun-maverick-miles-teller-goose-moustache-exclusive/|access-date=2022-01-24|website=Empire}}</ref>。

==早期生活==
泰勒出生於[[賓夕法尼亞州|賓夕法尼亞州]]的[[唐寧敦_(賓夕法尼亞州)|唐寧敦]]，母親梅里（Merry，娘家姓）是房地產經紀人，父親麥克·泰勒（Mike Teller）是核電廠工程師<ref name=vult1>{{cite web|last=Swanson|first=Carl|url=http://www.vulture.com/2014/01/miles-teller-on-that-awkward-moment.html|title=Miles Teller on Awkward, Fame, and Efron|publisher=Vulture|accessdate=2014-02-20|archive-date=2017-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170222104723/http://www.vulture.com/2014/01/miles-teller-on-that-awkward-moment.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他的父母都來自於[[新澤西州|新澤西州]][[卡尼斯點_(新澤西州)|卡尼斯點]]<ref name="rhprod">{{cite web|url=http://thecia.com.au/reviews/r/images/rabbit-hole-production-notes.pdf|title=Rabbit Hole presskit|format=PDF|accessdate=2012-04-23|archive-date=2014-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141105180845/http://static.thecia.com.au/reviews/r/rabbit-hole-production-notes.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Michael Williams/Today's Sunbeam|url=http://www.nj.com/sunbeam/index.ssf?/base/news-5/123968581427960.xml&coll=9|title=Man with local ties on ABC show Wednesday|publisher=NJ.com|date=2011-11-01|accessdate=2012-04-23}}</ref>。他有兩個姊姊<ref>{{cite web|last=Greco|first=Patti|title=Miles Teller on The Spectacular Now, Moonwalking, and the Divergent–Hunger Games Comparisons|url=http://www.vulture.com/2013/08/miles-teller-divergent-spectacular-now-interview.html|publisher=Vulture.cocm|accessdate=2013-12-10|date=2013-08-27}}</ref>。他的祖父是[[俄羅斯猶太人|俄羅斯猶太人]]後裔<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vogue.it/en/l-uomo-vogue/cover-story/2015/02/10/dane-dehaan/|title=Miles Teller|work=Vogue Italia - L'Uomo Vogue|date=2015-02-10|accessdate=2018-05-08}}</ref>。他的其他祖先還包括[[英國|英國]]、[[愛爾蘭|愛爾蘭]]、[[波蘭|波蘭]]和[[法國|法國]]的血統<ref>{{cite web|last=Miller|first=Gerri|url=http://www.interfaithfamily.com/arts_and_entertainment/popular_culture/Hollywood_Now_That_Awkward_Moment_Labor_Day_Somewhere_Slow.shtml|title=Hollywood Now: That Awkward Moment, Labor Day, Somewhere Slow|publisher=InterfaithFamily|accessdate=2014-02-20|archive-date=2014-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140209101019/http://www.interfaithfamily.com/arts_and_entertainment/popular_culture/Hollywood_Now_That_Awkward_Moment_Labor_Day_Somewhere_Slow.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=follers|url=http://ethnicelebs.com/miles-teller|title=Miles Teller profile at|publisher=Ethnicelebs.com|date=1987-02-20|accessdate=2014-02-20}}</ref>。

當泰勒還是個孩子時，因為父親工作的緣故，他們從原來的居住地[[西特拉斯縣|西特拉斯縣]]遷移到新澤西州的[[開普梅_(新澤西州)|開普梅]]<ref name="dailey">Dailey, Jennifer (April 14, 2009). [http://www.nj.com/sunbeam/index.ssf?/base/news-5/123968581427960.xml&coll=9 Man with local ties on ABC show Wednesday], NJ.com; accessed March 17, 2014.</ref>。在高中的時候，他曾當過薩克斯風手、地方教會青年組樂隊的鼓手和戲劇社的社長<ref name=vult1/><ref>{{cite web|last=Connor|first=Katie L.|title=Unexpected Crush Alert: Miles Teller|url=http://www.cosmopolitan.com/sex-love/hot-guys/miles-teller|work=[[Cosmopolitan_(magazine){{!}}Cosmopolitan|Cosmopolitan (magazine){{!}}Cosmopolitan]]|accessdate=2013-12-10|date=2013-08-30}}</ref>。於2005年，他從勒凱托中學（Lecanto High School）畢業<ref>{{cite web|last=Persall|first=Steve|title='Rabbit Hole' star Miles Teller brings good ol' boy vibe to 'Footloose' reboot|url=http://www.tampabay.com/incoming/rabbit-hole-star-miles-teller-brings-good-ol-boy-vibe-to-footloose-reboot/1195144|work=[[Tampa_Bay_Times|Tampa Bay Times]]|accessdate=2013-12-10|date=2011-10-08|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131214231559/http://www.tampabay.com/incoming/rabbit-hole-star-miles-teller-brings-good-ol-boy-vibe-to-footloose-reboot/1195144|archivedate=2013年12月14日}}</ref>。他在[[紐約大學|紐約大學]]帝許藝術學院獲得了美術學士學位<ref name="kaufman2010">Kaufman, Amy (December 28, 2010). [http://articles.latimes.com/2010/dec/28/entertainment/la-et-miles-teller-20101228 For Miles Teller, a role that was almost too real] {{Wayback|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2010/dec/28/entertainment/la-et-miles-teller-20101228 |date=20161012092405 }}, ''Los Angeles Times''; accessed March 17, 2014.</ref>。

==職業生涯==
麥爾斯·泰勒最初的電影處女作多為短片，直到2010年的《[[愛，讓悲傷終結|愛，讓悲傷終結]]》才開始出演正式電影。他曾在音樂劇《渾身是勁》的舞台上表演過<ref name="yamato">Yamato, Jen (November 8, 2010). [http://www.movieline.com/2010/11/miles-teller-on-diving-into-rabbit-hole-with-nicole-kidman-and-cutting-footloose.php Miles Teller on Rabbit Hole, Nicole Kidman and Cutting Footloose.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.movieline.com/2010/11/miles-teller-on-diving-into-rabbit-hole-with-nicole-kidman-and-cutting-footloose.php |date=20110820073519 }} ''[[Movieline|Movieline]]''</ref>。幾年後，他在同名音樂劇的改編電影《[[2011渾身是勁|2011渾身是勁]]》（[[肯尼·沃莫爾德|肯尼·沃莫爾德]]主演）中參演，而他所飾演的角色就和音樂劇的角色是一樣的<ref name="durbin">Durbin, Jonathan (2011). [http://www.interviewmagazine.com/film/miles-teller/ Miles Teller.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.interviewmagazine.com/film/miles-teller/ |date=20170719132614 }} ''[[Interview_(magazine)|Interview]]''</ref>。

2013年，他在由[[喬恩·盧卡斯|喬恩·盧卡斯]]與[[史考特·摩爾|史考特·摩爾]]聯合編導的《[[21玩過界|21玩過界]]》中出演<ref name="weinstein">Weinstein, Joshua L. (May 26, 2011). [http://www.thewrap.com/movies/column-post/miles-teller-enters-hangover-territory-27760 Miles Teller Joins Relativity's '21 and Over.'] ''[[The_Wrap|The Wrap]]''</ref>。同年，他與[[雪琳·伍德莉|雪琳·伍德莉]]合演的《{{le|戀夏進行式|The Spectacular Now}}》獲得了成功和矚目，這使泰勒獲得了2013年[[聖丹斯電影節|聖丹斯電影節]]評委會特別獎的戲劇類<ref>{{cite web|last=Hynes|first=Eric|title=2013 Sundance Film Festival Awards Updates|url=http://www.sundance.org/festival/blog-entry/2013-sundance-film-festival-awards|work=[[Sundance_Film_Festival|Sundance Film Festival]]|publisher=[[Sundance_Institute|Sundance Institute]]|accessdate=2014-01-18|author2=Jeremy Kinser |author3=Nate von Zumwalt |date=2013-01-26}}</ref>。2013年，他受到《[[英雄_(雜誌)|英雄]]》雜誌的專訪<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://store.hero-magazine.com/product/hero-9-suburban-heat-english |title="HERO 19: Suburban Heat” |accessdate=2014-09-06 |archive-date=2014-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140728033638/http://store.hero-magazine.com/product/hero-9-suburban-heat-english |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

他參演了2014年聖丹斯電影節的首映片《[[進擊的鼓手|進擊的鼓手]]》<ref>{{cite web|last=Gleiberman|first=Owen|title=Sundance: 'Whiplash' is the movie that could make Miles Teller a star|url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2014/01/17/whiplash-could-make-miles-teller-a-star/|work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|publisher=CNN|accessdate=2014-01-18|date=2014-01-17}}</ref>。在這之前，他也在同年的《[[約會進行時|約會進行時]]》和《[[分歧者_(電影)|分歧者]]》中亦有參與演出，其中《分歧者》是泰勒與伍德莉第二次共同參演的電影<ref>{{cite web|last=Gilchrist|first=Todd|title='Divergent' Star Miles Teller Had Fun Being A Jerk To Shailene Woodley|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/toddgilchrist/2013/11/06/divergent-star-miles-teller-had-fun-being-a-jerk-to-shailene-woodley/|work=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|publisher=Forbes publishing|accessdate=2014-01-19|date=2013-11-06}}</ref>。

2014年1月，泰勒將在[[史蒂芬·康拉德|史蒂芬·康拉德]]的無名[[約翰·貝魯西|約翰·貝魯西]]傳記片中詮釋[[丹·艾克洛德|丹·艾克洛德]]<ref>{{cite web|last=Kit|first=Borys|title=Miles Teller to Play Dan Aykroyd in Belushi Biopic, Says Star Emile Hirsch|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/miles-teller-play-dan-aykroyd-672270|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|publisher=[[Prometheus_Global_Media|Prometheus Global Media]]|accessdate=2014-01-19|date=2014-01-18}}</ref>。2014年2月，傳言他將在重啟版本的《[[驚奇4超人_(2015年電影)|驚奇4超人]]》中飾演[[神奇先生|神奇先生]]一角<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/miles-teller-kate-mara-fantastic-four-1201099921/|title=‘Fantastic Four’ Cast Revealed|last=Kroll|first=Justin|publisher=Variety|date=2014-02-19|accessdate=2014-02-20|archive-date=2014-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140904093243/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/miles-teller-kate-mara-fantastic-four-1201099921/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=‘What’s the Deal?’: Jeff Sneider on ‘Fantastic Four’ Casting, Fan Expectations (Video)|url=http://www.thewrap.com/whats-deal-jeff-sneider-fantastic-four-casting-video/|publisher=The Wrap|date=2014-02-21}}</ref>，而電影的拍攝工作於2014年8月已宣布殺青。2015年2月，宣布泰勒將和[[喬納·希爾|喬納·希爾]]共同主演[[陶德·菲利普斯|陶德·菲利普斯]]執導的《[[火線掏寶|火線掏寶]]》（2016年）<ref>{{cite news|url=http://deadline.com/2015/02/miles-teller-arms-and-the-dudes-whiplash-jonah-hill-1201372328/|title=‘Whiplash’ Star Miles Teller Joins Jonah Hill In ‘Arms And The Dudes’|last=Fleming Jr|first=Mike|date=2015-02-12|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|accessdate=2015-03-21}}</ref>。

==個人生活==
2007年，他曾出過一場車禍，這讓他的臉和脖子至今留下多處傷疤<ref>{{cite web|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2010/dec/28/entertainment/la-et-miles-teller-20101228|title=For Miles Teller, a role that was almost too real|work=Los Angeles Times|accessdate=2014-09-06|archive-date=2016-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161012092405/http://articles.latimes.com/2010/dec/28/entertainment/la-et-miles-teller-20101228|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年，泰勒與克萊·斯佩里（Keleigh Sperry）訂婚。<ref>{{cite web|title=Miles Teller (center) with his mother, grandmother and girlfriend Keleigh Sperry attend the Los Angeles Premiere of 'That Awkward Moment' Premiere, on Monday, January, 27, 2014 in Los Angeles. (Photo by Todd Williamson/Invision/AP)|url=https://in.lifestyle.yahoo.com/photos/miles-teller-center-mother-grandmother-girlfriend-keleigh-sperry-photo-082005078.html|access-date=2014-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812174147/https://in.lifestyle.yahoo.com/photos/miles-teller-center-mother-grandmother-girlfriend-keleigh-sperry-photo-082005078.html|archive-date=2014-08-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2019年9月1日兩人在夏威夷[[茂宜島|茂宜島]]結婚<ref>{{cite web|date=2019-09-02|title=Just Married in Paradise: See the First Photos From Miles Teller and Keleigh Sperry's Elegant Wedding in Maui|url=https://www.vogue.com/slideshow/see-the-first-photos-from-miles-teller-and-keleigh-sperry-wedding-in-maui|work=Vogue}}</ref>。

